OL,6,F"We are growing as the whole market is
OL,7,Fgrowing" she said.
OL,9,F"We've found it's not been as simply
OL,10,Fas beer drinkers, swapping for non-
OL,11,Falcoholic versions ` people are
OL,12,Ffinding new occasions to drink and
OL,13,Fsometimes switching between alcohol
OL,14,Ffree and alcohol.
OL,16,F"I think that's why we had a strong
OL,17,FDecember.
OL,19,F"People were happy to drink an
OL,20,Falcoholic beer one moment while with
OL,21,Ffriends but have one of ours the next."
