OL,3,CLucky Saint cheers sales jump after
OL,4,Cbumper December
OL,6,FShe said the company has benefited
OL,7,Ffrom an increase in people choosing to
OL,8,Fdrink non-alcoholic beer on weeknights
OL,9,Fand during the daytime.
OL,11,FThis has seen its cans of Lucky Saint
OL,12,Flager included in supermarket meal
OL,13,Fdeal offers as a result.
OL,15,FLucky Saint said December last year
OL,16,Fwas the group's largest sales month on
OL,17,Frecord amid a steady rise in demand
OL,18,Ffor the brand.
