OL,3,CLucky Saint cheers sales jump after
OL,4,Cbumper December
OL,6,FIt highlighted a particularly strong
OL,7,FChristmas period, with sales up 158%
OL,8,Ffor the week prior to Christmas in
OL,9,F2023 compared to the same week a year
OL,10,Fearlier.
OL,12,FThe brand said it was buoyed by many
OL,13,Fdrinkers switching between alcoholic
OL,14,Fand non-alcoholic drinks during
OL,15,Ffestive celebrations.
OL,17,FMs Heal said that the business feels
OL,18,Fthere is still plenty of room for the
OL,19,Fmarket to grow.
