OL,3,CLucky Saint cheers sales jump after
OL,4,Cbumper December
OL,6,F"In the UK, the amount of non-
OL,7,Falcoholic beer being bought is still
OL,8,Fsignificantly below levels elsewhere
OL,9,Fin Europe," she said.
OL,11,F"Currently in supermarkets it
OL,12,Frepresents about 6% of all beer and we
OL,13,Fcan see that growing towards 10%.
OL,15,F"And we are seeing a lot of growth
OL,16,Fpotential in pubs too.
OL,18,F"We have particularly found real
OL,19,Fmomentum there where we have been able
OL,20,Fto bring our draught beers to pubs."
