OL,3,CLucky Saint cheers sales jump after
OL,4,Cbumper December
OL,6,FNew research from the company
OL,7,Fhighlighted a change in the habits of
OL,8,Falcohol consumption in the UK,
OL,9,Fparticularly in hospitality venues.
OL,11,FIt found that almost two-thirds, 62%,
OL,12,Fof Britons said they feel comfortable
OL,13,Fto go to the pub without drinking
OL,14,Falcohol.
OL,16,FHowever, this found that women were
OL,17,Fparticularly more comfortable without
OL,18,Falcohol, at 69%, compared to only 56%
OL,19,Fof men.
